Summary: Saw a brilliant starlike UFO, as bright as the moon.
divs: Sighting DetailsI was putting trash out, and always notice the stars, this was briliant, bright, fiery almost. I thought this was not a star, could it be a brilliant asteroid or comet, I Checked sky and telescope and their were to be no odd, events that night. I was hugh. The moon was in the eastern sky a bit south. I seemed low, like a bit higher than our mountains. It was like a chunk of the moon fell off. Took a few pics, you will see how low it really was.
